<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }
        .container {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            border-radius: 5px;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
        }
        h1 {
            color: #ff6347;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .home-link {
            color: #3399cc;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .home-link:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>404 Not Found</h1>
        <p>Oops! The page you're looking for could not be found.</p>
        <p>It seems like you've stumbled upon a broken link or entered a URL that doesn't exist on our server.</p>
        <p>Please go back to our <a href="/" class="home-link">homepage</a> or use the navigation above to find what you need.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
